===Etymology 1===
[[image:Bee on flower.jpg|right|200px|Photo of bee]]
{{OE.}} ''[[beo|bēo]]'', from {{Ger.}} ''*bēō'', from {{IE.}} ''*bhī-''. Cognate with Dutch ''[[bij]]'', dialectal German ''[[Beie]]'' ([[w:Upper German|Upper German]]), Swedish ''[[bi]]''; and (''from Indo-European'') with Latvian ''[[bite]]'', Russian ''[[пчела]]'', Old Irish ''[[bech]]''.

